snippet.title: Sega Master System - Cyborg Hunter (1988) The most interesting game on the SMS
snippet.description: The most interesting  game , from the crap piles of SMS games... but those elevators, with no explanation how to use them , but when you get it how to use those ... you realise its a MegaMan Clone , with some added themes to not looks like a knock-off
